intent.user_query: For each product type, what is the average unit price at which the products were sold?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, AVG(sd.UnitPrice) FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductType;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductType, AVG(sd.UnitPrice) FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductType;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
